Christabel Ekeh (a mụrụ n'ọnwa Ọktoba 16, 1990) bụ onye Ghana na-eme ihe nkiri na ihe nlereanya
E gosipụtala ya na ihe karịrị ihe nkiri iri asatọ nke Ghana na Naijiria.
Ekeh malitere ọrụ ya dịka onye nlereanya ma sonye na asọmpi ịma mma, Miss Malaika Ghana afọ 2008 wee merie ọkwa nke abụọ.
Ọrụ ime ihe nkiri ya malitere mgbe ọ pụtara na ihe nkiri Naijiria College Girls
A makwaara ya maka ihe nkiri Potomanto
